data.description: Recently updated 4 bedroom home in highly sought after Guyer High School District! New carpeting on the stairs and all areas upstairs. New lighting in the foyer. New stove in the kitchen. Refrigerator conveys with the property. Plenty of space for the entire family with the primary bedroom downstairs and all secondary bedrooms upstairs. Additionally, there is a second living room upstairs with a media area. The pool table, bar and stools, and projector and screen convey with the property as an extra bonus. Relax and unwind in the backyard with a beautiful pool. Great corner lot!
